    <string name="aboutapp"><![CDATA[Welcome to Carbon View! \n🌍 Your companion for tracking and reducing carbon emissions in your business. Our app is designed to help small-to-medium businesses in industries like manufacturing monitor their carbon footprint and get actionable AI-powered suggestions. 📈\n\nFeatures:\n\nEmission Tracking 📊: Monitor Scope 1, Scope 2, and Scope 3 emissions with real-time data from IoT devices.\n\nAI-Powered Suggestions 💡: Get personalized recommendations to reduce emissions using Google’s Gemini API.\n\nDetailed Reports 📑: Download daily, weekly, or monthly emission reports.\n\nDevice Insights 🔍: Analyze emissions from specific devices like vehicles and appliances.\n\nUser-Friendly Design 📱: Simple navigation with clear, actionable insights.\nCarbon View is here to help your business achieve sustainability goals and reduce its environmental impact! 🌱]]></string>
